---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ResumeWithCareer"
  description="Read the ResumeWithCareer privacy policy to understand how we handle your resume data, what information we collect, and how we protect your privacy."
  path="/privacy-policy"
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="page-updated">Last updated: July 11, 2026</p>

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how ResumeWithCareer ("we", "us", "our")
    handles information when you use our website at
    resumewithcareer.com (the "Service"). By using the Service, you agree
    to the practices described in this policy.
  </p>

  <h2>Resume Processing</h2>
  <p>
    When you upload a resume for analysis, it is processed entirely in
    your browser using client-side technology. Your resume file is
    <strong>not uploaded to, or stored on, our servers</strong>. Once you
    close or refresh the page, the extracted resume text is discarded.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>
    ResumeWithCareer does not require account creation and does not
    collect personal information such as your name, email, or resume
    content on our servers. We may collect limited, non-identifying
    technical information (such as browser type and general usage
    patterns) through standard web hosting logs or analytics tools, solely
    to understand and improve the Service.
  </p>

  <h2>Local Storage &amp; Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    We use your browser's local storage to remember your theme preference
    (light or dark mode). This information stays on your device and is
    not transmitted to us.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    We may use third-party hosting or analytics providers to run and
    improve the Service. These providers may process limited technical
    data (such as IP address or browser information) under their own
    privacy policies.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Security</h2>
  <p>
    Because resume content is processed locally in your browser and not
    transmitted to our servers, the risk of your resume data being
    exposed through our systems is minimized. We nonetheless take
    reasonable measures to protect the Service from unauthorized access.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    The Service is not directed to children under 13, and we do not
    knowingly collect personal information from children.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be
    posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
    <a href="mailto:kumkumsisodiya7355@gmail.com">kumkumsisodiya7355@gmail.com</a>
    or visit our <a href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a> page.
  </p>
</SiteLayout>